      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلْعَبْدُ لاَ يُوَرَّثُ وَ اَلطَّلِيقُ لاَ يُوَرَّثُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5737 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Ali ibn Ri'ab who said that Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"A slave does not inherit, and a divorced person does not inherit.\""
        ]
      }
